title: Looking for Silver/Gold Team to join.
body:
Am currently Silver 5 solo queue, should be a lot higher not being cocky just the way it is (elo hell) and looking for a serious team to join that plays quite a lot as i am available most of the day usually towards the afternoon and all night. Brisbane based. Can play nearly anywhere but mainly prefer Jungle/ADC/MID the most. Just send me a message on here or add me and just message me when im green :)
IGN - vTreaatz
